data.name: Effects of Being High- A Study
data.abstract: This research study examines the effects of a marijuana induced high on test subjects. Collating results from over 50 participants, the study attempts to investigate the correlation between the psychoactive influence of marijuana and commonly associated phenomena such as delayed reactions, changes in brain activity, increase in appetite and markedly positive dispositions.

data.name: The Art of Goalscoring
data.abstract: In this research paper we reveal the main footballing principles that are combined to create a goal of skill and not luck, using data shown by studies involving 200 clips of footage, processed by high complexity AI technology. The scope of the study is limited to Italy
